OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBrook House: Ex-detainee   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fdescribes 'riot shield     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fattack'                    
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A former detainee has told a public    
OL,6, inquiry into an immigration centre how 
OL,7, officers in riot gear entered his cell 
OL,8, and attacked him with a shield.        
OL,10,FThe Brook House Inquiry heard the      
OL,11,Fincident happened as the man's cellmate
OL,12,Ffaced being moved to another centre.   
OL,14,FThe man, who cannot be named for legal 
OL,15,Freasons, said he became aware of what  
OL,16,Fmight happen when he saw five or six   
OL,17,Fmen outside the cell on 5 June 2017.   
OL,19,F"They were the most feared crew in     
OL,20,Fdetention," he said.                   
